title: Brandoll
description: Fen has just been assigned a position in the Special Dispatch Force protecting the King of Vera Morgan. When he arrives at the office for the "SDF", Fen realizes that he's been accidentally enrolled in the Special Doll Force instead! Fen discovers to his dismay that his new job is to search out and retrieve "bran dolls" with the help of four strange but beautiful men – who have more than just the job on their minds!
